          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The (g,p) and (g,n) differential yields  at  90 degree",
                " have been measured for  two-body  photodisintegration",
                " of He-4  using  tagged photons of energy Eg = 25 - 60",
                " MeV. Data   for   both   channels    were    obtained",
                " simultaneously using  windowless  ede  telescopes  to",
                " detect the  H-3  and  He-3  recoils.  The  ratio   of",
                " angle-integrated yields   which   is  insensitive  to",
                " systematic uncertainties due to the  simultaneity  of",
                " the measurements,  agrees with calculations employing",
                " only charge-symmetric  nuclear  interactions.  Within",
                " the present  errors  the  data  show no evidence of a",
                " significant charge-symmetry  violation  in  He-4   in",
                " energy range studied."
              ]
            }
          ],
